						               													<description>Windmill: Cute Secrets is a standalone expansion for Windmill: Cozy Stories and is fully compatible with Windmill: Cozy Stories. You can freely combine cards from both games to make your sessions easier or more difficult, or just more fun to play!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Windmill: Cute Secrets is a standalone expansion for the storytelling game Windmill: Cozy Stories. In Windmill: Cute Secrets, players are weaving short stories based on the hidden picture cards they draw.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;While one player tells a story, the other players attempt to guess the visible card that matches the story. The more opponents guess the card incorrectly, the more points the storyteller receives when a player finally guesses the right card. However, if all players fail to guess the picture, the storyteller loses a point instead, so the tale mustn't be too mysterious.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
